	<h1 class="title">传奇影业迎来万达这个新老板，《环太平洋2》等大片受益</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">彭卡茜 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-01-12 13:25:39 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
